Package stocker.view.chart

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChartRenderer
    The ChartRenderer class inherits from ChartRendererBase, is responsible for the actual drawing and implements the predefined render passes.
    ChartRendererBase
    The abstract class ChartRendererBase defines the basic variables, helpers and initialization methods as well as the signatures of the various render passes.
    ChartRendererVisualProfile
    Visual profile for the ChartPainter class.
    ChartView
    The chart view is responsible for the graphic display of the stock chart information.
    DialogAlarm
    The alarm dialog gives the user the option to add or remove new alarms.
    DialogAlarmTriggered
    Defines the alarm triggered dialog.
    DialogIndicator
    The indicator dialog gives the user the option to add or remove new indicators.
    DialogIndicatorParameter
    The indicator parameter dialog, to get user input for the indicator dialog.
    DialogViewBase
    Base class for all dialog frames
    MenuBarChart
    Menu bar of the chart view
